1
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,320
Young Master, Miss Song is here.

2
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:51,280
Which Miss Song?

3
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,000
The one from the General's Manor.

4
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,600
The one His Majesty ordered you to marry.

5
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:56,200
Young Master, it's too late!

6
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:22,160
You think you're worthy of proposing with such weak skills?

7
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:22,890
Do you yield?

8
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,280
I yield! I yield!

9
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,160
Go! Hurry!

10
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,020
Song Xuan, receive the edict.

11
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,720
By the Emperor's decree.

12
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:51,720
The Song family has sacrificed their lives for the country.

13
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:54,120
I pity their orphaned daughter, Song Xuan.

14
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:56,360
I hereby issue this decree.

15
00:02:56,360 --> 00:03:00,520
To betroth her to Bai Manchuan, son of the Marquis of Loyalty.

16
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:02,400
Respect this.

17
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:16,220
Bai Manchuan of the Marquis of Loyalty's Manor.

18
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:19,200
Miss, you can't marry him.

19
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,520
I heard that Bai Manchuan...

20
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,520
is nothing but a dissolute playboy.

21
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,360
He knows nothing of poetry or songs.

22
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,400
But he excels at drinking, gambling, and whoring.

23
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,720
His Majesty's decision...

24
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,680
is pushing you into a living hell.

25
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,160
Is he rich?

26
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,000
Does he have power?

27
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:33,880
Yes, that too.

28
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,860
That's enough.

29
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,520
Where is Bai Manchuan right now?

30
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:41,240
Life is short, enjoy it while you can.

31
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,040
Lord Bai.

32
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:25,960
Wait.

33
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:29,960
This scene inspires the poet in me.

34
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,690
Let me compose a poem first.

35
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:38,040
Xuelan, Xuelan, you're the wildest.

36
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:41,960
Outshining the phoenix in the Golden Tower.

37
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:46,320
One sway of your dance steals my soul.

38
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,120
I lie on the floor,

39
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,640
crying for mommy.

40
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,610
You call that a poem?

41
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,960
It's utter rubbish.

42
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,600
Why is it so quiet?

43
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:02,480
Great poem! Great poem, Lord Bai!

44
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:06,680
I, Lord Bai, will pay for everything tonight!

45
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,040
Great!

46
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:14,280
Thank you for your generosity, Lord Bai.

47
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,320
Lord Bai.

48
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:17,580
Shall Xuelan dance another solo for you?

49
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,440
Is this how you serve guests?

50
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,760
Are you blind?

51
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,880
Slapping your face actually hurts.

52
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:32,159
Your face is thicker than cowhide.

53
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:34,490
Bai Manchuan, you dare hit me, the Prince?

54
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,400
So what?

55
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,440
I did.

56
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,400
Even my father doesn't dare hit me!

57
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,200
I'll report you to the Emperor tomorrow!

58
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,360
And have him punish you for bullying royalty.

59
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,520
Go ahead. I don't care.

60
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,040
Lord Bai.

61
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,800
Thank you for earlier.

62
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,040
No big deal.

63
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:58,360
I despise those who bully women.

64
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,280
Scum.

65
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:01,280
Lord Bai, you're so bad.

66
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,640
I love it.

67
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:06,880
Let the music play! Keep dancing!

68
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:15,160
Where is Bai Manchuan?

69
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,640
Miss Song, what are you doing here?

70
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,320
Lord Bai isn't here.

71
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:35,720
Miss Song! Miss Song!

72
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,380
Let me catch my breath.

73
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:47,240
Lord Bai seems very dissatisfied with this decree.

74
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,280
Of course I am.

75
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,680
What are you doing now?

76
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,040
Since you're dissatisfied,

77
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,570
there is only one solution.

78
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:58,840
Do you yield?

79
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,760
My two little ancestors,

80
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,120
let's stop fighting, okay?

81
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,440
Matters between husband and wife,

82
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:05,040
why make such a scene?

83
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,760
Do you yield?

84
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,600
Are you crazy?

85
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,840
Come home with me.

86
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,540
Who's going home with you?

87
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,440
They just left like that?

88
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:34,040
The Marquis's silver at the border...

89
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,159
couldn't have just grown wings and flown away.

90
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:37,320
Do not mention this again.

91
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:39,159
Master, play your tile.

92
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,000
Eight of Dots.

93
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,240
Help me, Dad!

94
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:46,960
Hurry!

95
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,000
Son!

96
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,800
Quick, quick!

97
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:52,760
Which son of a bitch dared to hit my son?

98
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,280
Tell me.

99
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,200
I'll handle it for you.

100
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,159
It's... it's...

101
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:55,760
It was me.

102
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,640
It's her!

103
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,300
Greetings, Lord Marquis.

104
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,460
My good daughter-in-law.

105
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,120
All of you, get out.

106
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:08,580
Daughter-in-law, you're finally here.

107
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:11,280
Is there something wrong with your brain?

108
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,000
Hit him.

109
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:15,760
My dear, from now on, Manchuan...

110
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,760
is in your hands.

111
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,000
If he disobeys,

112
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,330
teach him a good lesson.

113
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,520
Just don't beat him to death.

114
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:24,160
Dad, I'm your biological son!

115
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,120
I must be dreaming.

116
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:32,880
Now it's just the two of us.

117
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,480
What do you want to do?

118
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,679
Men and women should keep their distance!

119
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,640
Don't try anything funny!

120
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:39,880
What about my pure and innocent reputation?

121
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:40,799
Is that so?

122
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:50,200
Help!

123
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:59,400
Who is going to pay for Young Master Bai?

124
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,640
Madam.

125
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,640
You can't even do a small thing right.

126
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,160
Spare us, Miss Shen.

127
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:16,290
How dare you let him do your dirty work?

128
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,520
And you.

129
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,400
You were so slow.

130
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:24,640
Did you have other intentions?

131
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:30,440
Miss Shen, please have mercy!

132
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,880
The plan was perfect.

133
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,570
Every single one of you,

134
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,200
is useless.

135
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,770
Useless things don't deserve to live.

136
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,400
It's our fault.

137
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,330
We didn't expect Miss Song to come.

138
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:49,680
You saw it too.

139
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:52,140
Young Master Bai clearly went unwillingly.

140
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,480
Damn Song Xuan.

141
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,800
If anyone dares to breathe a word about today,

142
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,200
I'll rip her mouth apart.

143
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,880
My precious daughter, does it hurt?

144
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:09,440
So pitiful.

145
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,880
So pitiful.

146
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:13,760
It was obviously Miss Song who took Young Master Bai.

147
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,290
Why did she take it out on us?

148
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,040
What a pity.

149
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:19,840
Young Master Bai caught the eye of such a demoness.

150
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:22,080
A demoness meets a bane star.
